Good morning, for the London flight at 10:30, 
you’ll have a 2 hour stopover in Amsterdam. 
You’re very late!!! 7
You have less than 1 minute to check-in at desk C! 
And make sure you have your passport and 
reservation ready.
Hello there. Passport and reservation please.

Thank you Sir.
 Let me check everything… 
Oh! You’re very late!
 Put your big luggage on the scales 
in order to process to the check-in. 
Your flight to London will take off soon!!
Go at boarding gate n°03. Run!

Good afternoon, 
Could you open your baggage, please ? 
Do you have anything to declare ?
 If not, you can go.
 Thank you very much and have a nice day.
